    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute beauty! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, it still feels brand new. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014spotless interior, flawless paint, and it drives like a dream. It\u2019s truly a rare find for someone who wants that 'just off the lot' feeling without the new car price tag. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
