    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, feeding power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this chassis is beyond reproach: the subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearing service is documented, addressing all critical S54 failure points. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback through the steering rack. Zero deferred maintenance, no fluid seepage, and a flawless underside make this a true turn-key collector piece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Clean title.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen that redefines the term 'showroom quality.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, mirror-like paint finish completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a state of absolute preservation; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and the original factory scent lingers. Every electronic component and driver aid functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is concours-level clean, and the undercarriage reflects a life spent on dry roads. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Complete with all original manuals, two keys, and a comprehensive service portfolio.",
      "price": 44500.0,
