    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including professional subframe reinforcement and a full Vanos system overhaul to ensure timing precision. The chassis remains remarkably taut, featuring an active M Variable Differential Lock and original suspension geometry that delivers exceptional lateral feedback. The exterior retains its factory-correct luster with no evidence of clear coat failure or panel misalignment. This is a turn-key, collector-spec machine for the purist who demands mechanical transparency and peak performance.",
